[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0973","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0973.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0652","title":"多款数据库服务暴露导致的信息泄露风险配置","description":"CVE-1999-0652 已被撤销（REJECT），原内容描述的是数据库服务（如 SQL Server、Oracle、MySQL 等）直接暴露在网络上的不安全配置问题。攻击者通过网络扫描可发现开放数据库端口，在未授权情况下尝试弱口令或默认凭证登录，进而窃取、篡改或删除敏感数据。此类风险属于安全配置缺陷而非软件漏洞，故该编号已被弃用，相关配置建议已纳入通用配置枚举（CCE）。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0652"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:55:00.253","remediation":"不应将数据库服务直接暴露在公网，应将数据库绑定到 127.0.0.1 或内网 IP，通过防火墙限制 1433（SQL Server）、1521（Oracle）、3306（MySQL）等端口的入站流量，仅允许受信任的应用服务器 IP 访问。同时启用强身份认证、禁用默认账户，并定期更新数据库补丁。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0973.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0972","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0972.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1130","title":"Netscape Enterprise Server JHTML 文件源码泄露漏洞","description":"Netscape Enterprise Server 3.5.1及3.6版本中搜索引擎的默认配置存在信息泄露漏洞。远程攻击者无需认证即可通过构造特制的搜索请求，利用HTML-tocrec-demo1.pat模式文件读取服务器上JHTML文件的源代码，导致敏感信息（如数据库连接参数、业务逻辑配置等）泄露。该漏洞影响Netscape Enterprise Server多个版本，攻击复杂度较低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1130"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:47.070","remediation":"Netscape Enterprise Server 已停止维护且不再提供安全更新。建议立即迁移至受支持的 Web 服务器（如 Apache HTTP Server、Nginx 或 IIS）。作为临时缓解措施，可删除或重命名默认搜索配置中的 HTML-tocrec-demo1.pat 模式文件，并限制对搜索功能的访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93346448121208&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93337389603117&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/559","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19443"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0972.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0972.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0971","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0971.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0651","title":"Unix R系列服务远程未授权访问漏洞","description":"rsh/rlogin 服务默认不加密传输所有数据，包括用户凭据和命令内容，且其基于 IP 地址的信任认证机制极易被伪造。攻击者可通过网络嗅探截获明文凭据，或通过 IP 欺骗绕过信任认证直接远程登录目标主机执行任意命令。该问题影响所有运行 rsh/rlogin 服务的 Unix/Linux 系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。修复方法为禁用 rsh/rlogin 服务，改用 SSH 等加密协议。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0651"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:47.017","remediation":"禁用 rsh/rlogin 服务：在 inetd/xinetd 配置中注释或删除 shell/login 服务条目，执行 `systemctl disable rsh.socket rlogin.socket`（systemd 系统）或重启 inetd 服务。使用 SSH 替代 rsh/rlogin 进行远程管理，在防火墙上阻断端口 513/tcp（rlogin）和 514/tcp（rsh）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2995"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0971.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0970","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0970.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1129","title":"Cisco Catalyst 2900 VLAN交换机 未授权VLAN遍历漏洞","description":"Cisco Catalyst 2900 系列虚拟局域网交换机中存在 IEEE 802.1q VLAN 遍历漏洞。远程攻击者可通过伪造中继标签中的 VLAN 标识符，向其他 VLAN 注入 802.1q 帧，从而打破 VLAN 隔离机制实现跨 VLAN 访问。该漏洞允许攻击者无需认证即可绕过网络隔离策略，窃取或篡改不同 VLAN 中的敏感数据。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1129"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:46.940","remediation":"将所有非 trunk 端口设为静态 access 模式（`switchport mode access`），禁用 DTP（`switchport nonegotiate`），并在 trunk 端口上启用 VLAN 修剪（`vlan pruning`）以及限制允许的 VLAN 列表（`allowed vlan`）。同时配置本征 VLAN 为未使用的专用 ID 并关闭自动协商。这些措施可阻断伪造 802.1q 帧跨 VLAN 攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cisco.com/univercd/cc/td/doc/product/lan/28201900/1928v8x/eescg8x/aleakyv.htm","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/26008","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/615","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3294","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1129.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1129","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1129.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1129.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/79c2cf4630fcc44f2632735de08432a07cfaf204/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-29q9-4h2h-9p7g/GHSA-29q9-4h2h-9p7g.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/615/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1129.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--ecbfddda-04a3-4138-b1cd-3892ec7d91fd.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--ecbfddda-04a3-4138-b1cd-3892ec7d91fd.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0970.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0969","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0969.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0650","title":"Unix Netstat 服务信息泄露漏洞","description":"netstat 服务（TCP 端口 15）默认开放且未限制访问来源，远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标系统的 netstat 服务发送查询请求，获取当前网络连接状态、路由表、网络接口及协议统计信息。该服务的信息泄露特性使攻击者能够收集内网拓扑结构、活跃连接和服务部署情况，为后续网络嗅探、中间人攻击或针对性渗透提供情报支撑。受影响系统包括运行 netstat 服务的各类 Unix/Linux 发行版。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0650"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:46.887","remediation":"关闭系统上不必要的 netstat 服务，在 inetd.conf 中注释或删除 netstat 行后重启 inetd 进程；对外部网络在防火墙层面阻断对 netstat 端口（默认 15/tcp）的访问；若需保留本地使用，可移除 setuid 权限并将 netstat 的访问限制为仅 root 用户。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/72"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0969.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0968","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0968.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0649","title":"FSP 文件传输服务暴露漏洞","description":"FSP（File Service Protocol）服务运行在目标主机上，该协议未对文件传输提供认证或加密机制。攻击者可通过网络远程访问该服务，可能导致未授权文件读取、写入或信息泄露。该问题属于安全配置缺陷，而非软件漏洞，通常建议在不必要时禁用该服务或通过防火墙限制其访问。CCE（Common Configuration Enumeration）更适用于此类配置问题分类。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0649"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:55:00.207","remediation":"建议关闭 FSP 服务（File Service Protocol），或通过防火墙限制仅允许受信 IP 访问端口 21/TCP。若业务需要文件传输功能，应替换为 SFTP 或 SCP 等加密协议，避免使用明文传输的 FSP 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0968.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0967","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0967.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0648","title":"通用 X.25 服务运行配置问题（此编号已废弃，不构成安全漏洞）","description":"tags.<value>CVE-1999-0648 候选编号已被驳回，原因为该条目描述的是\"X25 服务正在运行\"这一系统配置状态，并非直接引入安全漏洞的缺陷类型。此类配置类问题更适合收录于通用配置枚举（CCE）体系。该候选编号不应被用于安全漏洞追踪，其 CVSS 评分为 0，不具备实际可利用的攻击条件。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0648"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:55:00.170","remediation":"如非必要，建议在系统配置中禁用 X.25 服务（如 Solaris 中停止 x25 相关 daemon，Linux 中移除或封锁 x25 内核模块），或在网络边界防火墙封禁 TCP 端口 2000/2001 以限制外部访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0648.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0648","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0648.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0648.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/5c36feecacaa0eef96caef76eb433e2bf57c7235/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0648.json","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-1999.jsonl","https://github.com/cmjayasinghe/Threat-Intelligence-Dashboard/blob/ccfec8014cc85c9e776b8f657bdb7879139ab5ed/data/cves.csv","https://github.com/Software-Engineering-2026-Class/kelompok4-cyber-kg-agentic/blob/0fc3a7d1e2416617ef834c956997e1f0f283424b/parser_agent/output/cve.ttl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0967.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0966","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0966.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0647","title":"UNIX bootparamd 服务运行配置问题","description":"bootparamd（引导参数服务）是一种基于 RPC 的传统网络服务，用于向无盘客户端提供引导参数。该服务运行于系统中时，可能被远程攻击者利用来探测网络配置与主机信息，造成信息泄露。由于其本身不直接引入安全漏洞，更适合归入通用配置枚举（CCE）进行管理。建议在非必要环境中禁用该服务以减少攻击面。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0647"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:55:00.137","remediation":"建议在服务器上禁用 bootparamd 服务，该服务用于无盘工作站启动，在现代网络中已无必要且可能泄露系统信息。执行 `killall bootparamd` 并禁止随系统启动（删除或注释相关 inetd 条目）。若确实需要，应在防火墙中限制 RPC 端口 (111/udp) 仅允许受信任子网访问，或配置 hosts.allow/hosts.deny 进行访问控制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0647.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0647","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0647.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0647.json","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000468.txt","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/5c36feecacaa0eef96caef76eb433e2bf57c7235/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0647.json","https://github.com/aboutcode-org/aboutcode-mirror-euvd/blob/1b758e4b71978ff973a6df1bc69fc70b932735fb/advisories/2000/02/EUVD-1999-0630.json","https://github.com/cmjayasinghe/Threat-Intelligence-Dashboard/blob/ccfec8014cc85c9e776b8f657bdb7879139ab5ed/data/cves.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0966.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0965","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0965.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0646","title":"LDAP 服务配置暴露风险","description":"CVE-1999-0646 已被撤销（REJECTED），不再作为安全漏洞使用。该候选编号的原始描述为 LDAP 服务正在运行，仅涉及 LDAP 协议服务的配置暴露情况，并非直接的安全漏洞，不满足 CVE 漏洞收录标准。NVD 官方说明指出该条目更适合归入通用配置枚举（CCE）体系进行管理，因此该编号已被废弃。此条目不涉及任何可利用的安全缺陷，不存在攻击条件或利用方式。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0646"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:55:00.103","remediation":"如非业务必需，建议禁用 LDAP 匿名绑定，配置 LDAPS（LDAP over SSL/TLS）代替明文 LDAP（端口 389），并在防火墙层面限制只有信任网络可访问 LDAP 端口（389/636）。同时启用访问控制列表（ACL）和账户密码策略，防止信息泄露。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0646.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0646","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0646.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0646.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/5c36feecacaa0eef96caef76eb433e2bf57c7235/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0646.json","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-1999.jsonl","https://github.com/cmjayasinghe/Threat-Intelligence-Dashboard/blob/ccfec8014cc85c9e776b8f657bdb7879139ab5ed/data/cves.csv","https://github.com/Software-Engineering-2026-Class/kelompok4-cyber-kg-agentic/blob/0fc3a7d1e2416617ef834c956997e1f0f283424b/parser_agent/output/cve.ttl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0965.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0964","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0964.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0645","title":"IRC 服务运行信息泄露漏洞","description":"CVE-1999-0645 已被拒绝使用，原分配描述为\"IRC 服务正在运行\"，该条目实质描述的是系统中 IRC 服务处于启用状态的配置信息，而非本身存在安全漏洞。由于此类配置枚举更适合归入通用配置枚举（CCE）体系，NVD 已将其标记为 REJECT 状态。系统管理员应关注 IRC 服务是否确实需要运行，若无需使用建议关闭以减小攻击面。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0645"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:55:00.070","remediation":"在服务器上禁用不必要的 IRC 服务。Linux 系统执行 systemctl disable ircd 并停止对应服务；Windows 系统通过 services.msc 将 IRC 相关服务设为禁用。在边界防火墙上封禁 IRC 默认端口 6660-6669/TCP 的出站流量，防止内网主机外连 IRC 服务器。定期使用端口扫描确认 6660-6669 端口无对外开放。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0645.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0645","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0645.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0645.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/5c36feecacaa0eef96caef76eb433e2bf57c7235/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0645.json","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-1999.jsonl","https://github.com/cmjayasinghe/Threat-Intelligence-Dashboard/blob/ccfec8014cc85c9e776b8f657bdb7879139ab5ed/data/cves.csv","https://github.com/Software-Engineering-2026-Class/kelompok4-cyber-kg-agentic/blob/0fc3a7d1e2416617ef834c956997e1f0f283424b/parser_agent/output/cve.ttl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0964.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0963","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0963.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1126","title":"Cisco Resource Manager 信息泄露漏洞","description":"Cisco Resource Manager (CRM) 1.1 及更早版本创建文件时使用了不安全的权限设置，导致本地攻击者可读取 swim_swd.log、swim_debug.log、dbi_debug.log 以及名称以 \"DPR_\" 开头的临时文件，从中获取包含用户名、密码和 SNMP 团体字串在内的敏感配置信息。该漏洞攻击复杂度低，但需要系统本地访问权限，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1126"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:46.547","remediation":"将 Cisco Resource Manager 升级至 CiscoWorks Resource Manager Essentials (RME) 后续受支持版本；同时立即对 swim_swd.log、swim_debug.log、dbi_debug.log 及 DPR_* 临时文件设置仅 root 可读权限（chmod 600），并清除日志中明文存储的用户名、密码及 SNMP 团体字串；限制仅授权管理员具有本地系统访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/i-086.shtml","http://www.cisco.com/warp/public/770/crmtmp-pub.shtml","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1575","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1126.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1126","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1126.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1126.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1126.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87017/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1126.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--ea4986e5-e053-4e4f-b784-9c4adf62a083.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idinfor"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0963.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0960","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0960.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0642","title":"Multiple Vendors POP Service 未授权访问漏洞","description":"该漏洞条目原描述为目标系统运行了 POP（Post Office Protocol）邮件服务，该服务默认监听 TCP 110 端口。运行 POP 服务本身并不构成直接安全漏洞，但在配置不当（如未启用加密、使用弱口令认证、暴露于公网）的情况下，远程攻击者可能通过暴力破解或会话劫持等方式获取邮件内容，导致敏感信息泄露。该条目已被 CVE 官方驳回，认为其属于通用配置枚举（CCE）范畴而非安全漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0642"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.973","remediation":"如非业务必需，建议在服务器上禁用 POP3 服务（如 CentOS: `systemctl disable dovecot`；Ubuntu: `systemctl disable pop3`）；如确需使用，限制仅允许加密连接（启用 TLS/SSL，设置 `ssl = required`），并在防火墙层面限制仅允许受信 IP 访问 TCP 端口 110。同时建议使用 IMAPS（端口 993）替代明文 POP3。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0642.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0642","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0642.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0642.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/5c36feecacaa0eef96caef76eb433e2bf57c7235/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0642.json","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-1999.jsonl","https://github.com/cmjayasinghe/Threat-Intelligence-Dashboard/blob/ccfec8014cc85c9e776b8f657bdb7879139ab5ed/data/cves.csv","https://github.com/Software-Engineering-2026-Class/kelompok4-cyber-kg-agentic/blob/0fc3a7d1e2416617ef834c956997e1f0f283424b/parser_agent/output/cve.ttl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0960.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0959","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0959.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1124","title":"Adobe ColdFusion HTTP客户端安全绕过漏洞","description":"Allaire ColdFusion 中的 mainframeset.cfm 页面存在安全绕过漏洞。该页面提供的 HTTP 客户端功能允许远程攻击者提交目标 URL，服务器会代表攻击者向内网其他端口上的 Web 页面发起请求，由于请求来源被伪造为本地回环地址（localhost），因此可以绕过基于 IP 地址或端口的访问控制策略。攻击者无需身份认证即可利用此漏洞扫描内网端口、访问内部受限资源，导致敏感信息泄露或进一步的横向攻击。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1124"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:46.283","remediation":"升级至 ColdFusion 5.0 或更高版本（该版本修复了 mainframeset.cfm SSRF 绕过问题）；若无法升级，在 Web 服务器（IIS/Apache）层面通过 URL 重写规则或访问控制列表（ACL）禁止外部请求访问 /mainframeset.cfm 路径；同时在防火墙上限制应用服务器对外部端口的出站连接，防止被利用为内网探测代理。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstorm.securify.com/mag/phrack/phrack54/P54-08","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1124.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1124","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1124.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1124.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1124.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/79c2cf4630fcc44f2632735de08432a07cfaf204/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-c8gw-jg28-8m4v/GHSA-c8gw-jg28-8m4v.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1124.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/7ae10c2036875bb5ef530e18322e7ca2477ed16c/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0959.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0958","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0958.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0641","title":"Multiple Unix UUCP 服务远程安全漏洞","description":"UUCP（Unix-to-Unix Copy Protocol）服务默认在 TCP 端口 540 上运行，该服务设计上缺乏充分的身份认证机制，远程攻击者可在无需认证的情况下通过 UUCP 协议与目标系统建立连接，执行文件传输、远程命令执行等操作，导致系统被未授权访问。该问题影响早期运行 UUCP 服务的多种 Unix 系统，攻击者利用此服务可窃取敏感文件或控制系统，危害严重。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0641"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:46.627","remediation":"立即停止并禁用 UUCP 服务（uucp/uucico），执行 `systemctl stop uucp && systemctl disable uucp`（或对应 init 脚本 `service uucp stop && chkconfig uucp off`）。如业务必须使用，应配置 TCP Wrapper（/etc/hosts.allow 和 /etc/hosts.deny）限制可信来源 IP，并在防火墙上关闭 TCP 540 端口。若无需 UUCP 功能，建议直接卸载 uucp 软件包。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0641","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0641.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0641","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0641.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0641.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0641.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/79c2cf4630fcc44f2632735de08432a07cfaf204/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5v9j-2mwh-j984/GHSA-5v9j-2mwh-j984.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0641.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153200_153300.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0958.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0957","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0957.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1117","title":"IBM AIX lquerypv 本地文件读取漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 4.1 及 4.2 系统中的 lquerypv 工具在解析 -h 命令行参数时未对文件路径进行充分校验，导致存在任意文件读取漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向 -h 参数传入目标文件路径（如 /etc/passwd 或系统配置文件），越权读取本无权访问的敏感文件内容，造成信息泄露。该漏洞利用条件要求攻击者拥有本地 shell 访问权限，虽然无需 root 权限但无法远程触发，故整体危害较低，CVSS 评分 2.1。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1117"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:45.383","remediation":"升级 IBM AIX 至 4.3 或更高版本，IBM 已通过 APAR 修复此问题。如无法升级，以 root 执行 `chmod 755 /usr/sbin/lquerypv` 移除 setuid 权限，阻止普通用户以特权运行该命令。同时通过文件系统 ACL 限制可执行 `lquerypv` 的用户范围作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/h-13.shtml","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167420195&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167420196&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&w=2&r=1&s=lquerypv&q=b","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/455","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1752","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19345","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1117.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1117","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1117.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1117.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1117.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/79c2cf4630fcc44f2632735de08432a07cfaf204/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g9xm-g3q5-pm76/GHSA-g9xm-g3q5-pm76.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1117.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000997.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581